{"synckey":1658291200,"updated":[{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_26_441-462","chapterUid":26,"markText":"ORDER BY还支持按相对列位置进行排序","range":"441-462","createTime":1658291200,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_24_1965-2072","chapterUid":24,"markText":"注意：ORDER BY子句的位置在指定一条ORDER BY子句时，应该保证它是SELECT语句中最后一条子句。如果它不是最后的子句，将会出错。","range":"1965-2072","createTime":1658291148,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_24_1333-1364","chapterUid":24,"markText":"ORDER BY子句取一个或多个列的名字，据此对输出进行排序。","range":"1333-1364","createTime":1658291006,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_24_1174-1225","chapterUid":24,"markText":"SQL语句由子句构成，有些子句是必需的，有些则是可选的。一个子句通常由一个关键字加上所提供的数据组成。","range":"1174-1225","createTime":1658291001,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_19_1927-2131","chapterUid":19,"markText":"SELECT prod_name    FROM Products    LIMIT 5 OFFSET 5;分析▼LIMIT 5 OFFSET 5指示MySQL等DBMS返回从第5行起的5行数据。第一个数字是检索的行数，第二个数字是指从哪儿开始。这个语句的输出是：","range":"1927-2131","createTime":1658270696,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_19_1508-1705","chapterUid":19,"markText":"如果你使用MySQL、MariaDB、PostgreSQL或者SQLite，需要使用LIMIT子句，像这样：输入▼    SELECT prod_name    FROM Products    LIMIT 5;","range":"1508-1705","createTime":1658270666,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_19_1112-1508","chapterUid":19,"markText":"SELECT prod_name    FROM Products    FETCH FIRST 5 ROWS ONLY;分析▼FETCH FIRST 5 ROWS ONLY就会按字面的意思去做的（只取前5行）。如果你使用Oracle，需要基于ROWNUM（行计数器）来计算行，像这样：输入▼    SELECT prod_name    FROM Products    WHERE ROWNUM <=5;","range":"1112-1508","createTime":1658270650,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_19_539-580","chapterUid":19,"markText":"在SQL Server中使用SELECT时，可以用TOP关键字来限制最多返回多少行","range":"539-580","createTime":1658270586,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_18_1102-1197","chapterUid":18,"markText":"SELECT DISTINCT vend_id告诉DBMS只返回不同（具有唯一性）的vend_id行，所以正如下面的输出，只有3行。如果使用DISTINCT关键字，它必须直接放在列名的前面。","range":"1102-1197","createTime":1658270556,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_18_895-932","chapterUid":18,"markText":"办法就是使用DISTINCT关键字，顾名思义，它指示数据库只返回不同的值。","range":"895-932","createTime":1658270504,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_17_447-498","chapterUid":17,"markText":"SELECT语句还可以检索所有的列而不必逐个列出它们。在实际列名的位置使用星号（＊）通配符可以做到这点","range":"447-498","createTime":1658270437,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_16_595-648","chapterUid":16,"markText":"在选择多个列时，一定要在列名之间加上逗号，但最后一个列名后不加。如果在最后一个列名后加了逗号，将出现错误。","range":"595-648","createTime":1658270365,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_15_618-699","chapterUid":15,"markText":"上述语句利用SELECT语句从Products表中检索一个名为prod_name的列。所需的列名写在SELECT关键字之后，FROM关键字指出从哪个表中检索数据。","range":"618-699","createTime":1658270352,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_14_721-765","chapterUid":14,"markText":"为了使用SELECT检索表数据，必须至少给出两条信息——想选择什么，以及从什么地方选择。","range":"721-765","createTime":1658270342,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_15_1773-1826","chapterUid":15,"markText":"请注意，SQL语句不区分大小写，因此SELECT与select是相同的。同样，写成Select也没有关系。","range":"1773-1826","createTime":1658269427,"type":1},{"bookId":"34336685","bookmarkId":"34336685_15_1288-1328","chapterUid":15,"markText":"如果没有明确排序查询结果（下一课介绍怎样指定顺序），则返回的数据没有特定的顺序。","range":"1288-1328","createTime":1658269407,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"3.3 按列位置排序","chapterUid":26,"chapterIdx":26},{"title":"3.1 排序数据","chapterUid":24,"chapterIdx":24},{"title":"2.6 限制结果","chapterUid":19,"chapterIdx":19},{"title":"2.2 检索单个列","chapterUid":15,"chapterIdx":15},{"title":"2.1 SELECT语句","chapterUid":14,"chapterIdx":14},{"title":"2.3 检索多个列","chapterUid":16,"chapterIdx":16},{"title":"2.4 检索所有列","chapterUid":17,"chapterIdx":17},{"title":"2.5 检索不同的值","chapterUid":18,"chapterIdx":18}],"book":{"bookId":"34336685","version":205299065,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://wfqqreader-1252317822.image.myqcloud.com/c